Package: moby
Title: Streamlined Acoustic Telemetry Analyses and Data Visualization
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: person("Miguel", "Gandra", , "m3gandra@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
                  comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-1506-5141"))
Description: Provides a comprehensive suite of functions and methods specifically tailored
    for processing, visualizing, and interpreting passive acoustic telemetry data,
    with a particular focus on marine environments. Tools span data cleaning, temporal
    and spatial classification, movement and home-range analysis, residency metrics,
    and spatiotemporal overlap and social-network analysis.
